Seekers: Mother, what is Sahaja Yoga?

00:10:15.656 --> 00:10:17.240
Shri Mata ji: Sahaja Yoga

00:10:17.280 --> 00:10:20.475
Sahaja.
‘Saha’ means with, ‘ja’ means born.

00:10:20.500 --> 00:10:22.723
‘Sahaja’ means
‘It is born with you.’

00:10:22.760 --> 00:10:24.323
Yoga is born with you.

00:10:24.380 --> 00:10:26.490
So that you have the right.

00:10:26.540 --> 00:10:31.189
It is your birth right
to get union with God.

00:10:31.220 --> 00:10:33.006
It's your birth right.

00:10:33.040 --> 00:10:34.790
You are born with Sahaja.

00:10:34.820 --> 00:10:36.140
It has a double
meaning as you know.

00:10:36.180 --> 00:10:37.673
Sahaja also means union.

00:10:37.700 --> 00:10:41.223
But actually the word Sahaja
comes from this ‘Sa-ha-ja.’

00:10:41.260 --> 00:10:43.273
Saha means with, ja means born.

00:10:43.300 --> 00:10:45.090
Born with you.

00:10:45.140 --> 00:10:49.540
And Sahaja in our talking we
say Sahajme, means easily.

00:10:49.580 --> 00:10:52.373
Because it is born with you.
We are breathing now

00:10:52.400 --> 00:10:54.140
so easily

00:10:54.180 --> 00:10:58.240
Because it is born
with us, it is Sahaja.

00:10:58.280 --> 00:11:02.820
