to stand up on our heads or we had to

00:11:02.820 --> 00:11:07.035
say read books, we would
have been dead long time back.

00:11:07.060 --> 00:11:11.239
It comes Sahaja-spontaneous.

00:11:11.270 --> 00:11:14.790
We cannot do anything
about it, it's all done for you.

00:11:14.830 --> 00:11:18.056
